name: Cornify [Tumblr post icons]
description: Tumblr 'new post' icons for your dashboard. "Cornify started as a spoof of internet companies that are based around a single feature (specifically addthis.com) and receive millions of dollars in investment. The goal was to come up with the most ridiculous single-feature web company, which ended up being a web service for adding cheesy, glittery unicorns and rainbow graphics to any website." *
